            "answer_text": "Research is not about the Institute, its about your passion and your contribution. Even you can do Research in any top rank Institutes, what will be your imagination and your style of working and presenting it to the social welfare or some other thing which can be extended by your successors. Search for simple problems and simple solutions you can find your research area, see have have been done so far, what should be done. Do it, write it, code it, but they must be honest and it must be from yourself and present it. it will be a starting of good research. I can show you person who did PhD in top most institute with 0% contributions to the society. you can see people who did PhD in simple institutes who gave themselves to the world and was in Hall of Fame and got prestigious awards. Final Note : PhD is a not a degree, its a Passion. please enjoy it and follow it. ",
